<h2>komaletter: Simply Beautiful PDF Letters from Markdown</h2>
<p>Write beautiful yet versatile letters in R Markdown. PDFs are 
  generated using the 'KOMA-Script' letter class and the 'pandoc-letter' 
  template. 'KOMA-Script' caters to the international writer. It provides 
  layouts for many common window envelope types (e.g. German, US, French, 
  Japanese) and allows you to define your own. The package comes with a default
  layout based on 'DIN 5008B'.</p>
